.TH FLOWGATE 1 "December 2025" "1.0.0" "Flowgate Manual"
.SH NAME
flowgate \- Network Flow Controller (DNS & Proxy Manager)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B flowgate
.RI [ options ] " command"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B flowgate
is a modern CLI tool for managing network flow infrastructure, including DNS (Blocky/AdGuardHome) and Proxy (Nginx/Angie) servers.
.PP
It automates the configuration of domains, upstreams, and SSL certificates.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B status
Show the status of managed services.
.TP
.B sync
Synchronize configuration with the backend services.
